==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Irreproachable
<hw>Ir`re*proach"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>ir-</ets> not + <ets>reproachable</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>irr⟦eacute⟧prochable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not reproachable; above
reproach; not deserving reproach; blameless.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He [Berkely] erred, -- and who is free from error? -- but his
intentions were <qex>irreproachable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Beattie.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irreproachableness</ent>⟦br⟧
